  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study it to conduct a randomized, controlled, double-blinded trial of
      carbon dioxide (CO2) versus air insufflation during endoscopic retrograde
      cholangiopancreatography (ERCP).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
